EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO CRIMINAL OFFENSES -- WEAPONS
***
1 This act would add officers or employees of the United States authorized by law to carry a
2 concealed firearm, to the category of persons exempt from certain state laws regarding licenses,
3 permits, and certificates needed to carry a pistol or revolver, whether visible or concealed.
4 This act would take effect upon passage.
